### =========================================================
### Product Query Scenario
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN
@passportId = REPLACE_PASSPORT_ID

### 1) Get Asset State
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/state
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 2) Get Current Owner
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/owner
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) My Passports (소유 여권 목록)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/me/passports
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
